{"tid":746964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本KFC搞周五放題  1380yen炸雞任食！","createTime":"2018-07-18T04:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T17:38:11.000Z","uid":31314,"like":92,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"b313fc91369ca698ea955d35ad3f18a037a97638","tid":746964,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://sociorocketnewsen.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/kt-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsociorocketnewsen.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F06%2Fkt-1.png&h=1e03b1f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早幾年都聽過，日本KFC有放題任食，千幾yen有交易。<br />\n<br />\n不過分店地點唔算就腳，都係聽完就算。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n呢個夏天，日本「雞記」將呢個gimmick發揚光大，<br />\n<br />\n宣佈喺全國218間分店，逢星期五推出放題，當中47間喺東京，<br />\n<br />\n連涉谷、池袋、秋葉原、中野等等行街熱點，<br />\n<br />\n都有得嘆。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n日子由7月20至8月31日，只需1380yen，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就可以任食45分鐘炸雞、薯條、汽水、鬆餅！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小學生有特價，只需980yen。唔駛下下同佢地去築地食魚生，都滿足到爆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://sociorocketnewsen.files.wordpress.com/2018/07/ak-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsociorocketnewsen.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F07%2Fak-1.png&h=50bd395b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5586f994c2f991f15efd4e89f4ca85222873354","tid":746964,"uid":31314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"The promotion kicks off July 20 at 218 participating branches across Japan. 47 of those are in Tokyo, with the most centrally located being the KFC branches at Shibuya Dogenzaka, Akihabara, Asakusa, Ikebukuro, Ikebukuro Nishiguchi, Tokyo Dome City LaQua, Nakano, Hacchobori, Sangenjaya, and Eifukucho.<br />\n<br />\nEvery Friday between July 20 and August 31, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1,380 yen (US$12.30) gets you all the original recipe fried chicken you can eat for 45 minutes, plus as many orders of curly-cut French fries, biscuits, and soft drinks as you&rsquo;d like t go with it.</strong></span> The price for elementary school-age kids is discounted to 980 yen, and children younger than that eat for free when accompanied by a paying full-price customer (one free child per customer, with additional children eating for 680 yen each)."},{"pid":"823fe6024dc11b7e0b0b679fdf7200d28bad416d","tid":746964,"uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":79,"score":-70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"頂盡4件，其實唔平計番<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01d575ed25a75b8475d733a02320a1574438305","tid":746964,"uid":8883,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:21:59.000Z","msg":"無葡撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be93e94b619a29d72d59dacf32986c9272ef2145","tid":746964,"uid":12558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"😱😱😱"},{"pid":"e38b51e576805b2107d6e2472b4e0584fc7880d2","tid":746964,"uid":70988,"like":140,"dislike":3,"score":137,"quote":{"pid":"823fe6024dc11b7e0b0b679fdf7200d28bad416d","tid":746964,"uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":79,"score":-70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"頂盡4件，其實唔平計番<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"渣，我老母都食到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b607c78a47a4e9c6a3cf8771d0344e2f492ef58","tid":746964,"uid":1910,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"1380 yen 係香港一個人食都食到嘔"},{"pid":"04887dd25f768a071c5aa60bd5155b1da520de6c","tid":746964,"uid":39381,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:26:04.000Z","msg":"食完實生瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb9c71c8ec17629227117aaa